{"tid":1741641,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"11.24 區選注意事項","createTime":"2019-11-20T12:12:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-22T10:01:54.000Z","uid":200464,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"2af958c928b7821bdae491fc4f8a6b48fa783d90","tid":1741641,"uid":200464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T12:12:03.000Z","msg":"比較重要（一定要記得）：<br />\n1. 記得帶身份證明文件，e.g.身份證，護照etc <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n2. 以防政府中途腰斬投票程序，建議越早投越好，最好就投完票去食黃店早餐<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n3. 收到選票檢查有冇塗污 / 損壞，如果有記得要換過張<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n4. 印仔唔好吸出界，吸完要等一陣乾咗先好對摺選票<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DyXBs6A.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDyXBs6A.jpg&h=21fb7332&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">5.一票不投保皇黨</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"d2b90abc3fcfa0c031896225ab8b1375728df032","tid":1741641,"uid":181823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T14:06:11.000Z","msg":"[文宣組入] 請唔好幫候選人做文宣！犯法仲會累人坐監！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1728047\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1728047</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"71a4ba4ac7e92cd49ee965204e44f4c7aa319c2e","tid":1741641,"uid":305994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T14:14:40.000Z","msg":"11.24 區選有用link 各區候選人派系 有埋政綱及往績<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1740944\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1740944</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"73cf0949be33e71d18fff99e6982a87113331e20","tid":1741641,"uid":321238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T14:15:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/026FRTK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F02